original_title: Fille ou garçon, mon sexe n'est pas mon genre
overview: Being born a woman, feeling like a man & deciding to cross the boundary between the genders. That’s the path taken by those known as trans-boys. In San Francisco, Paris & Barcelona, a four-way portrait of Lynnee, Kaleb, Rocco & Miguel, four individuals who embody & explore the fluidity of gender.
title: Girl or Boy, My Sex Is Not My Gender
